name: Hangtime Art Zine
description:
Fake Your Own Death

Hang Time

Collaborative NBA-Focused Zine
Hangtime is a celebration for the beginning of the NBA basketball season.
Artists include Thom Lessner, Lori D, Nathan Mckee, Rob Doran, Rita Badalamenti, Bwana Spoons, Sam Coomes, Luke Yablonsky, Bruce Paulson, Brent Wick, Janet Weiss, Free Darko & more.
Each zine comes with a different team sticker and numbered players card.
To see more detailed images visit here http://cargocollective.com/fakeyourowndeath

name: Micheal Jackson, PE, Salt N Pepa, Run DMC, 2pac & Biggie button sets
description:
Nathan McKee has crafted a series of buttons that capture the fun and feeling of the music of our youth.

Nathan's pen and ink drawings are just the right touch of detail and style.

These one-inch buttons are the perfect addition to a lapel or hat or bookbag â€” and help show you know how to kick it old school.

From the King of pop to the East/West Biggie & 2pac to the Kings of Rock Run DMC & the Queens of hip hop Salt N Pepa & last but not least the political rap of Public Enemy.
 To see close up photos please go to http://cargocollective.com/fakeyourowndeath

 Make sure to specify which set you are buying.

name: Fake Your Own Death #2
description:
Not many zines have this varied of content; it's more like a multi-media art gallery you can carry around with you than a magazine.
Curated by Portland, Oregon's Nathan Mckee, Fake Your Own Death is a silk-screened cover, 32 page zine that contains a CD, two mini-zines, and a sealed envelope inside.
Features new, original work from:
- Tamar Mohait 
- Liz harris 
- Rita Badalamenti 
- Josh Sachs 
- Fremont Slim 
- Rob Doran 
- Nathan Mckee 
- Tim Root 
- Jessie Rose Vala.
To more images of content please go to http://cargocollective.com/fakeyourowndeath
